          "reviewBody": "Mindseed preschool & daycare is outstanding with the way they make the children's daily activities.\nI loved the way they teach the children's. The staff of the school is very much polite with the students. The method of the teaching is just awesome which makes your child make a progress everyday. Lucky to have admission at mindseed for my son.",
