            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best school and daycare in city. The have great approach for teaching. Child connects to the teachers and school. Teachers have great patience. Best part is kid is learning and connecting something new daily.\nThe school like this is blessing for strong foundation of the kid.\nAs daycare too.. they play they learn. One of the best part is no screen time.\nFor little kid it's another home.\nA great thanks to all the teachers and staff",
          "publisher": {
