            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best preschool and daycare in wakad area.. Staff and teacher are very caring..children enjoy being and communicating with teacher.\nMy child started daycare when he was just 1.8 year old and now he is also part of preschool.I see him enjoying and happy. Daycare teacher Anita ma'am made him so much comfortable that he started enjoying in school.She is loving and caring with all students.He even started talking after joining the daycare\nSchool take cares of any special need for child..\nThanks for providing best environment for children to grow.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
