          },
          "reviewBody": "Best preschool and daycare in wakad visited today for my childs admission .....received detailed information.....staff is caring there, also my child was served with lunch as he was hungry...that I felt was overwhelming....Thank you Mindseed.\nI wholeheartedly appreciate the efforts of the entire team of teachers at Mindseeds wakad for the wonderful service and a great experience.",
          "publisher": {
