          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Went there for an enquiry, however the maushi did not even open the gate. She informed me that 'madam' has gone for lunch. I asked whether someone else could attend me, as I could see some ladies sitting inside, to which she said no. She told that madam will come at 3.30pm\n\nIt was not at all a welcoming experience. They have not answered my calls nor the maushi took my number as if they do not need any business. Good that I got to experience this attitude before enrolling my baby.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
