        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Mindseed - Wakad"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Prashant Anand"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-04-01",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son attended nursery at Mindseed Wakad CP. If you arent aware, Mindseed runs just nursery to k2 and daycare, like many other preschools. But let me tell you whats unique about Mindseed in my opinion. The school is small and so is the student to teacher ratio. That means your little one gets one-on-one time with the teacher. I say so because my kid used to give a good deal of daily rundown of all the activities and great conversations he had with his teacher. He missed many school days due to frequent viral infections, almost a week of every month but his teacher made sure he didnt miss out on anything important because again, every kid at Mindseed gets taught invidually to a good extent. It made me feel so comfortable and at ease that I chose Mindseed over other schools, I knew his was in good hands.\n\nComing to extra curricular activities, I can bet that the sports and annual day events were as grand as any highly reputed school in Pune hosts every year.\n\nAdmitting Kabir to Mindseed was the best interests decision I took for him. Though we are moving to a new school now, its only because I dont have enough time to drop him off and pick him from the school, our new home is going to be almost 9kms away from the school premises.\n\nMy sincere thanks to his teacher/mentor and everyone at the school for making this journey so memorable for him.\n\nMy best wishes to team Mindseed!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Mindseed - Wakad"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Trupti Magdum"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-31",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Mindseed is the best choice for pre primary school and Daycare too.\n\nWakad Chaudhary park branch is very good...all teachers and Mawshi staff are very co operative\n\nActivities and celebration are best part along with studies, kids learn about all festivals.\n\nSchool has variety of study material and toys.\n\nI will highly recommend this school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
