          "reviewBody": "While screening the first school for our kid was hectic...but when we entered the Mindseed pre-school, instatly got clicked that this is best for our son. And now no regrets...thanks to Nainal mam, she took care of everything. Our son is very happy to go school. Always talking about Nainal mam and Asmita maushi.\nThanku❤️",
          "publisher": {
